<br>
Warslicks is a great place, in addition to the Sarnak fort in LOIO. I spent some time threre myself. Got a bit boring though. /Yawn. <br>
<br>
However, if you are SoL enabled a good place I found with the exception of some adds is Marus Seru. But you cant go there until you're at least 25. You can stay right by the entrance of the small tower there and pull Grey Rockhoppers solo with pet. Also some Stonebringers will con Blue but they hit hard and they appear to have a regen. <br>
<br>
You just need to be a bit careful as either of the two can add. Also, there are Zelniaks that con Blue but can also add. Do not wait for assistance with the guards. Since the hoppers and the Stonebringers are indiferent to you and when killing them there are no faction hits against you. The guards will not assist you if you find yourself in trouble. The only MOBS they will assist you with are the Zelniaks. So if you find yourself in a bit of a jam, run through the small tower and zone into Netherbians Lair. You are safe at the zone line. <br>
Don't expect good loot there or money, just experience and if you're a tailor the hides are usable. <br>
<br>
If you can do this, I found that I got some great experience in there. However, you need to be cautious. <br>
<br>
If you're not SoL enabled as of yet, The experience in LOIO and Warsliks far outweighs going to the Karanas. In those zones you are guaranteed to hit 30. <br>
<br>
